# NIX HASH
Nixpkgs: nixpkgs.nix
Source: https://github.com/NixOS/nix
Description: Compute and convert Nix hashes.
Version: nix --version

## Commands

### Basics
- nix hash path path/: Compute the SHA-256 hash of a directory.

### Essentials
- nix hash to-base32 sha256:abc...: Convert a hash to Nix's base32 format.
- nix hash to-sri --type sha256 abc...: Convert to SRI format (Subresource Integrity).

